description: Rare free-standing single-family home, custom built, ideally located near the Convention Center and Seaport District. This unique residence offers a perfect blend of privacy, luxury, and convenience, with direct access heated garage parking, tandem driveway space, and three outdoor areas—including two decks and a roof deck with 360° views of the Boston skyline. Inside, enjoy an open fireplaced living room and sleek kitchen with granite island, high-end appliances, and custom cabinetry. A fully finished family room, on a different floor from the bedrooms, offers added privacy and flexibility.  Additional highlights include high ceilings, surround sound systems through out, three spacious bedrooms including a luxurious primary suite with gas fireplace. Located in South Boston’s desirable West Side, just minutes from the T, parks, Foodie’s Market, restaurants, and highways—this is refined city living at its best.
